<i>noun</i>: 웃옷 [우돋], 겉옷 [거돋] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>웃옷 [우돋]</dt><br>
<dd>outerwear</dd><br>
<dd>가장 겉에 입는 옷.</dd><br>
<dd>The clothes worn over one's innerwear.</dd><br>
<dt>겉옷 [거돋]</dt><br>
<dd>1. outerwear</dd><br>
<dd>겉에 입는 옷.</dd><br>
<dd>Clothes worn over one's innerwear.</dd><br>
<dd>2. outer garments</dd><br>
<dd>추위를 막기 위해 겉에 걸쳐 입는 옷.</dd><br>
<dd>Clothes worn over other clothes to keep one's body warm when it is cold outside.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>